# character traits

character progression is defined by its traits.

the traits are 12 values ranging from -16 to 15 that control how the character will level up and which actions to choose

traits:

- physical / magical
- offensive / defensive
- supportive / attacker
- risky / cautious
- fire / water
- wind / earth
- light / darkness
- chaos / order
- sly / honorable
- range / melee
- absorb / inflict
- area / focus

stats and skills are automatically selected based on these bits

at the end of the run, the player can also explore the actual progression ("path") chosen by the hero


